#       Hien Phap v5.0 Dieu 7 (audit bat bien) + Dieu 8 (EventBus single source)

[scope]
problem_summary:
  Tep KHO TS hien dang chua hon hop hai luong event:
    - Fixed asset records (ASSET_INVENTORY_updated)
    - System operational logs (SYSTEM_LOG_emitted, vd WARN_RESTORE)
  Vi pham single-responsibility per cell boundary.
  Vi pham Dieu 7+8 Hien Phap v5.0.
  Quantum Defense khong the aggregate signal chinh xac do noise pollution.

[severity]
HIGH (constitutional violation)

[required_split]

service_1:
  cell:        business/inventory-cell
  service:     domain/services/asset-inventory.engine.ts
  emits:       ASSET_INVENTORY_updated
  consumes:    asset register data only (fixed assets, depreciation, status)
  excludes:    operational system logs

service_2:
  cell:        kernel/monitor-cell
  service:     domain/services/system-log.engine.ts
  emits:       SYSTEM_LOG_emitted
  consumes:    operational warnings (WARN_RESTORE, PROCESS_DAILY, etc.)
  excludes:    asset register data

[event_contract_dependency]
shared-contracts-cell phai canonical hoa truoc:
  - ASSET_INVENTORY_updated event contract
  - SYSTEM_LOG_emitted event contract
File contract dat tai:
  src/cells/business/shared-contracts-cell/domain/contracts/inventory.events.contract.ts
  src/cells/business/shared-contracts-cell/domain/contracts/monitor.events.contract.ts

[acceptance_criteria]
  1. Khong con cell nao subscribe ca hai event tu mot source
  2. asset-inventory.engine.ts khong import bat ky logger system nao
  3. system-log.engine.ts khong truy cap asset register
  4. boundary.policy.na cua hai cell phai phan tach ro:
       inventory-cell.canSendTo phai co audit-cell, KHONG co monitor-cell direct
       monitor-cell.canSendTo phai co audit-cell, KHONG co inventory-cell direct
  5. Quantum Defense receive 2 event types phan biet, signal-to-noise phuc hoi

[migration_path]
  Phase 1: Kim build asset-inventory.engine.ts (boundary clean)
  Phase 2: Kim build system-log.engine.ts (boundary clean)
  Phase 3: Bang verify khong cross-import via scanner
  Phase 4: Quantum Defense re-aggregate, confirm signal clean
  Phase 5: Audit-cell record reconciliation completion

[dependencies]
  - shared-contracts-cell event contract (BLOCKER)
  - audit-cell ready to receive split events (READY)
  - quantum-defense-cell THRESHOLD_REGISTRY entry update needed

[gatekeeper_decisions_required]
  - Approve split spec
  - Sprint allocation for Kim
  - Optional: archive cu KHO TS file vao _deprecated/ sau migration

[bang_role_post_implementation]
  - Run scanner detect cross-import violation
  - Verify 4 acceptance criteria
  - Record reconciliation completion vao audit trail
